    "faq": [
      {
        "question": "How long does it take to build my website?",
        "answer": "Most VB Specialty Launchpad sites are live within 1-2 weeks. Because I've built 100+ sites, I have a proven component library that accelerates delivery without sacrificing quality."
      },
      {
        "question": "Do I need to provide content and images?",
        "answer": "I'll guide you through exactly what's needed. Most clients provide their business info and photos, and I handle the rest — copywriting, layout, and optimization."
      },
      {
        "question": "Will my site actually rank on Google?",
        "answer": "Every site includes local SEO setup: Google Business Profile optimization, schema markup, and fast Netlify edge-delivery. These are the fundamentals that move the needle for local search."
      },
      {
        "question": "What about booking and scheduling?",
        "answer": "Integrated booking is a core feature. I use serverless functions to connect your site with scheduling tools, so customers can book directly — no friction, no phone tag."
      },
      {
        "question": "What if I need changes after launch?",
        "answer": "Your site is built on modern, maintainable technology. I offer ongoing support and can make updates quickly. You're not locked into a rigid template."
      }
    ]
