        "content_full": [
          "Reusable copy is not copy-paste. I use frameworks so every page has clear structure, then I rewrite the language so it sounds like the actual owner and market.",
          "[IMAGE: Side-by-side copy drafts for three different local businesses with shared structure but distinct tone and keywords, annotated edits in red and blue.]",
